for personal reasons,

00:00:35.350 --> 00:00:38.260
Greisa Martinez cannot
be with us today.

00:00:38.260 --> 00:00:43.760
And we're all very
saddened about that.

00:00:43.760 --> 00:00:46.690
Let me introduce the moderator
of our panel, Ambassador

00:00:46.690 --> 00:00:48.640
Samantha Power.

